{"id": "art-111", "label": "Art. 111", "title": "Art. 111", "slug": "art-111", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_196022679\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1285\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_196022679\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 111 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1895199386\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1284\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1895199386\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Timpul de munc&#259; reprezint&#259; orice perioad&#259;\nîn care salariatul presteaz&#259; munca, se afl&#259; la dispozi&#355;ia\nangajatorului &#351;i î&#351;i îndepline&#351;te sarcinile &#351;i\natribu&#355;iile, conform prevederilor contractului individual de munc&#259;,\ncontractului colectiv de munc&#259; aplicabil &#351;i/sau ale legisla&#355;iei\nîn vigoare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1439362557\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1283\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1439362557\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Programul de munc&#259; reprezint&#259; modelul de\norganizare a activit&#259;&#355;ii, care stabile&#351;te orele &#351;i zilele\ncând începe &#351;i când se încheie prestarea muncii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_675968816\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1282\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_675968816\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Modelul de organizare a muncii reprezint&#259; forma de\norganizare a timpului de munc&#259; &#351;i repartizarea sa în func&#355;ie de\nun anumit model stabilit de angajator.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}